==English==
===Proper noun===
'''[[Aotearoa]] [[New Zealand]]'''
#(''New Zealand'') A [[bicultural]] name for New Zealand.
# [[New Zealand]] often referred to a the Land of The Long White Cloud or Godzone

===Alternative spellings===
'''Aotearoa-New Zealand'''

====Quotations====
"The Commission recognises the importance of M&#257;ori culture... to all people of Aotearoa New Zealand" (Human Rights Commission Focus, March 1988).

